items.title: Awesome Privacy
items.content_text:
### Captchas

*   [mCaptcha](http://mcaptcha.org/) ([repo (⭐2.3k)](https://github.com/mCaptcha/mCaptcha)) - An open-source CAPTCHA system with seamless UX.  mCaptcha uses SHA256 based proof-of-work (PoW) to rate limit users.
items.content_html:
Captchas

  • mCaptcha (repo (⭐2.3k)) - An open-source CAPTCHA system with seamless UX. mCaptcha uses SHA256 based proof-of-work (PoW) to rate limit users.

items.title: Discount for Student Dev
items.content_text:
### IDE and Code Editing

*   [GitHub Codespaces](https://www.github.com/codespaces/)\[FREE] - An online IDE for GitHub that provides a complete dev environment with a single click. Free personal plan subscription for as long as you are a student via [Github Student Developer Pack](https://education.github.com/pack).
items.content_html:
IDE and Code Editing

  • GitHub Codespaces[FREE] - An online IDE for GitHub that provides a complete dev environment with a single click. Free personal plan subscription for as long as you are a student via Github Student Developer Pack.

items.title: Awesome LaTeX
items.content_text:
### Docker Images

*   [dante-ev/docker-texlive (⭐109)](https://github.com/dante-ev/docker-texlive) - debian-based full TeXLive system with additions with pandoc, perl, and python pre-installed

### Books / TikZ

*   [Formatting Information (2020)](https://latex.silmaril.ie/formattinginformation) - This is the HTML5-based online version of the book *Formatting Information - An introduction to typesetting with LATEX*. It has been continuously updated since the early 2000s.
items.content_html:
